  <summary date="2018-09-05T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Reaching English Learners Act

This bill amends the Higher Education Act of 1965 to establish a grant program to pay the federal share of the costs for preparing teachers to effectively instruct English learners. Grants may be awarded for up to five years.</summary>
